    "Name": "Ranger RGR-1X",
    "Details": "The RGR-1X is the original Ranger configuration, built around an entirely ammunition-free energy loadout designed for sustained operations far from resupply lines. Two arm-mounted Light PPCs provide reach at longer ranges, while two left-torso ER Medium Lasers and a right-torso Medium Pulse Laser handle mid-range engagements. Two ER Small Lasers and a pair of center-torso ER Flamers discourage close approach. Eighteen Double Heat Sinks support continuous fire across the full weapons suite.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Energy</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
